imum amount of rent outstanding on the tenancy.\\n\\nRegent Letting and Property Management Limited are members of the UKALA Total Loss Client Money Protection Scheme, and are also members of The Property Ombudsman redress scheme. You can find out more details on our website   or by contacting us directly. \",\"displaySize\":\"\",\"showOnMap\":true,\"propertyUrl\":\"/properties/163944971#/?channel=STU_LET\",\"contactUrl\":\"/student-accommodation/contactBranch.html?propertyId=163944971\",\"staticMapUrl\":null,\"channel\":\"STUDENTS_RENT\",\"firstVisibleDate\":\"2025-06-30T09:51:33Z\",\"keywords\":[],\"keywordMatchType\":\"no_keyword\",\"saved\":false,\"hidden\":false,\"onlineViewingsAvailable\":false,\"lozengeModel\":{\"matchingLozenges\":[]},\"streetView\":{\"showStreetView\":true},\"enquiredTimestamp\":null,\"updateDate\":\"2025-06-30T09:57:04Z\",\"enquiryAddedTimestamp\":null,\"enquiryCalledTimestamp\":null,\"enhancedListing\":false,\"propertyImages\":{\"images\":[{\"srcUrl\":\"https://media.rightmove.co.uk:443/dir/crop/10:9-16:9/88k/87187/163944971/87187_52262_IMG_00_0000_max_476x317.jpeg\",\"url\":\"88k/87187/163944971/87187_52262_IMG_00_0000.jpeg\",\"caption\":\"Kitchen\"},{\"srcUrl\":\"https://media.rightmove.co.uk:443/dir/crop/10:9-16:9/88k/87187/163944971/87187_52262_IMG_01_0000_max_476x317.jpeg\",\"url\":\"88k/87187/163944971/87187_52262_IMG_01_0000.jpeg\",\"caption\":\"Bathroom\"},{\"srcUrl\":\"https://media.rightmove.co.uk:443/dir/crop/10:9-16:9/88k/87187/163944971/87187_52262_IMG_02_0000_max_476x317.jpeg\",\"url\":\"88k/87187/163944971/87187_52262_IMG_02_0000.jpeg\",\"caption\":\"Balcony\"},{\"srcUrl\":\"https://media.rightmove.co.uk:443/dir/crop/10:9-16:9/88k/87187/163944971/87187_52262_IMG_03_0000_max_476x317.png\",\"url\":\"88k/87187/163944971/87187_52262_IMG_03_0000.png\",\"caption\":\"Open plan\"},{\"srcUrl\":\"https://media.rightmove.co.uk:443/dir/crop/10:9-16:9/88k/87187/163944971/87187_52262_IMG_04_0000_max_476x317.png\",\"url\":\"88k/87187/1639